Prove that 
\begin_inset Formula $z(x\bmod y)=(zx)\bmod(zy)$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
answer 
\end_layout

\end_inset

If 
\begin_inset Formula $z=0$
\end_inset

