\begin_inset Formula $\frac{x}{y}-1<\frac{x}{y}-\frac{z}{y}=k\leq\frac{x}{y}$
\end_inset

,
 which means that 
\begin_inset Formula $k=\lfloor\frac{x}{y}\rfloor$
\end_inset

